question: Within a radius of 90 kilometers, where can I find  a fast food restaurant on the path leading to Embassy Suites, Altamonte Springs, FL from Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens, Sanford, FL?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.314867 28.825462)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.385792 28.664796)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.314867 28.825462)',4326)::geography, 90000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.314867 28.825462)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Nestle Toll House | Edy's Ice Cream

[3].display_name: Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens, Sanford, FL
